###

# @name user-with-recipe
GET {{user_base_url}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

# @name updating
PUT {{user_base_url}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "name": "somente o nome"
}

###

# @name delete
DELETE {{user_base_url}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

